#
# Item definitions for the discoverable item system.
#
# Each item is a prefab-style label tagged `type: item/<category>/<sub>` so it
# is found by labels_get_type("item/") - no new syntax. The body is the effect:
# it runs server-side (via upgrade_add in item_activate.mast) with UPGRADE_AGENT_ID
# (the holder) and the metadata fields available as variables (key, duration...).
# Effects use modifier_add on the engine's *_upgrade_coeff keys (default 1.0,
# additive value = bonus fraction) and auto-expire after `duration` - replacing
# the old console-side delay_app loops (which had reset typos).
#
# metadata fields:
#   type      item/<category>/<sub>   (category: upgrade | resource | ...)
#   key       stable id (matches the legacy inventory key / pickup role)
#   art       pickup art_id
#   mode      consumable | install | resource
#   targets   agent kinds it can apply to
#   consoles  console(s) that may activate it (omit = any)
#   duration  consumable effect length (seconds)
#   tier/price economy hints (placeholder until Phase 5/6)
#

=== prefab_item_carapaction_coil
metadata:``` yaml
type: item/upgrade/defense
key: carapaction_coil
display_text: Carapaction Coil
art: alien_2a
mode: consumable
targets: ship, cockpit
consoles: weapons, engineering
duration: 300
tier: 2
price: 250
desc: Reinforces shields (3x) for a time.
```
    modifier_add(UPGRADE_AGENT_ID, "all_shield_upgrade_coeff", 2.0, key, duration=duration)
    ->END

=== prefab_item_infusion_pcoils
metadata:``` yaml
type: item/upgrade/helm
key: infusion_pcoils
display_text: Infusion P-Coils
art: danger_4a
mode: consumable
targets: ship, cockpit
consoles: helm
duration: 300
tier: 2
price: 250
desc: Boosts impulse and turn (3x) for a time.
```
    modifier_add(UPGRADE_AGENT_ID, "impulse_upgrade_coeff", 2.0, key, duration=duration)
    modifier_add(UPGRADE_AGENT_ID, "turn_upgrade_coeff", 2.0, key, duration=duration)
    ->END

