=== prefab_item_secret_codecase
metadata:``` yaml
type: item/upgrade/comms
key: secret_codecase
display_text: Secret Codecase
art: container_1a
mode: consumable
targets: ship, cockpit
consoles: comms
duration: 300
tier: 3
price: 400
desc: Arms a one-shot enemy auto-surrender (used from comms).
```
    set_inventory_value(UPGRADE_AGENT_ID, "sc_armed", 1)
    signal_emit("item_codecase_armed", {"holder_id": UPGRADE_AGENT_ID})
    ->END

=== prefab_item_hidens_powercell
metadata:``` yaml
type: item/resource/energy
key: hidens_powercell
display_text: HiDens Power Cell
art: container_2a
mode: resource
targets: ship, cockpit
desc: Instantly restores 500 ship energy when used.
```
    blob = to_blob(UPGRADE_AGENT_ID)
    if blob is not None:
        blob.set("energy", blob.get("energy", 0) + 500, 0)
    ->END

